459
00:20:45,407 --> 00:20:47,382
Est-ce qu'il y a quelqu'un?

460
00:20:47,417 --> 00:20:48,751
Personne?

461
00:20:48,997 --> 00:20:50,502
Hé ho?

462
00:20:51,875 --> 00:20:53,403
